    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's been kept in truly flawless condition, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
