    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless E46 M3, a true collector-grade specimen. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for superior lateral dynamics. This example features a reinforced rear subframe\u2014addressing the chassis's primary fatigue point\u2014and retains its original factory-spec suspension geometry. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, free of imperfections, while the undercarriage is devoid of oxidation. This is a mechanically transparent, high-performance icon for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
