    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a factory finish that retains its deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip, swirl mark, or blemish. The interior is a virtual time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or creasing, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, toggle, and digital display functions with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free from any signs of inclement weather exposure. This sale includes all original keys, the complete owner\u2019s manual set, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. For the discerning collector who demands perfection and accepts no compromises, this is the definitive choice.",
