      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for an adventure, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
