    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concourse-level condition. The S54 power plant remains naturally aspirated perfection, featuring a recently overhauled VANOS system and verified rod bearing service for absolute mechanical peace of mind. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe mounting points, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the finish retains its factory luster with zero orange peel or clear coat degradation. This example exhibits zero oil seepage, a perfectly balanced valve train, and a suspension geometry that remains tight and communicative. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking mechanical purity.",
